description: Funky Good Time: The Anthology is a 2CD compilation by The J.B.'s originally released in 1995. The J.B.'s were James Brown's backing band, who performed and released names under numerous names, including Fred Wesley & The J.B.'s, Maceo & The Macks, and The Last Word. This set includes all nine of their chart hits and quite a few rare singles and long versions. Universal.
